{"id":1510,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":248,"title":"Conversation 128","subtitle":"Flight Delay at Check-In","level":"B1","parts":17,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-128.1510/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/0-conversation-128.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me,\nis this the check-in counter for Jetstars Airlines?\nI'm flying to Sydney.\nMy apology, sir.\nThe flight has been delayed due to a mechanical problem with the plane.\nAccording to the technicians, the estimated wait time is around 5 hours.\nUmm... That's not good.\nI have to make it to a fundraiser for a wildlife foundation in Australia this evening.\nCan you put me on the next flight?\nOf course.\nMay I see your passport and ticket?\nHere you go.\nI prefer a flight that arrives before noon and a business class seat.\nThanks!\nCertainly.\nJust one moment....\nlet me check your booking and see what I can do.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:49","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":0.86},{"position":2,"content":"is this the check-in counter for Jetstars Airlines?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/2.mp3","time_start":0.86,"time_end":3.94},{"position":3,"content":"I'm flying to Sydney.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/3.mp3","time_start":3.94,"time_end":5.25},{"position":4,"content":"My apology, sir.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/4.mp3","time_start":5.36,"time_end":6.98},{"position":5,"content":"The flight has been delayed due to a mechanical problem with the plane.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/5.mp3","time_start":6.98,"time_end":10.86},{"position":6,"content":"According to the technicians, the estimated wait time is around 5 hours.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/6.mp3","time_start":10.86,"time_end":15.75},{"position":7,"content":"Umm... That's not good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/7.mp3","time_start":15.75,"time_end":17.68},{"position":8,"content":"I have to make it to a fundraiser for a wildlife foundation in Australia this evening.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/8.mp3","time_start":17.68,"time_end":22.81},{"position":9,"content":"Can you put me on the next flight?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/9.mp3","time_start":22.81,"time_end":24.7},{"position":10,"content":"Of course.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/10.mp3","time_start":24.7,"time_end":25.92},{"position":11,"content":"May I see your passport and ticket?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/11.mp3","time_start":25.92,"time_end":28.04},{"position":12,"content":"Here you go.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/12.mp3","time_start":28.43,"time_end":29.5},{"position":13,"content":"I prefer a flight that arrives before noon and a business class seat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/13.mp3","time_start":29.7,"time_end":33.64},{"position":14,"content":"Thanks!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/14.mp3","time_start":33.64,"time_end":34.77},{"position":15,"content":"Certainly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/15.mp3","time_start":34.95,"time_end":36.04},{"position":16,"content":"Just one moment....","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/16.mp3","time_start":36.04,"time_end":38.23},{"position":17,"content":"let me check your booking and see what I can do.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-128-2024-09-14-18-07-08/17.mp3","time_start":38.23,"time_end":41.05}]}